rows.label: qst201611_msg0001
rows.name: Bravo! Bravo! A huge success, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0002
rows.name:
As expected of Nanakoori-san.
Everyone was moved by your song, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0003
rows.name: How was it, Nanakoori?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0004
rows.name: ...Yes, it felt really good.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0005
rows.name:
I feel like, through the song,
I became one with everyone!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0006
rows.name: I see. That's great!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0007
rows.name: Tora was moved too, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0008
rows.name: Why are you crying?!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0009
rows.name:
With this concert, Nanakoori-san's
popularity will skyrocket, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0010
rows.name:
Next, let's have everyone
hear Nanakoori-san's song on
an even bigger stage, mo.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0011
rows.name: A bigger stage?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0012
rows.name: Alba Margen, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0013
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0014
rows.name:
Alba Margen? The imperial
capital of Superbia?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0015
rows.name: That's right, mo. That Alba Margen, mo.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0016
rows.name:
A concert in the capital... I bet
a lot of people will gather.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0017
rows.name:
No one has ever held a concert
in Alba Margen before, mo.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0018
rows.name:
If she succeeds with a concert of this
scale, Nanakoori-san will be one of a kind,
the number one diva in the world, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0020
rows.name: Are you scared now?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0021
rows.name: ...Yes, it's very scary.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0022
rows.name:
But I want to try. I want
many people to hear my song.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0023
rows.name:
Yes, yes! That's the spirit,
mo! With this attitude, you'll
definitely succeed, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0024
rows.name:
...However, to negotiate
with the Empire, we need
to gather more fans, mo.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0025
rows.name: How many?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0026
rows.name: We need at least 5,000 fans, mo.

rows.label: qst201611_msg0027
rows.name: That many?! Isn't that impossible?

rows.label: qst201611_msg0028
rows.name:
It's fine, mo! The current
Nanakoori-san can gather
that many in no time, mo!

rows.label: qst201611_msg0029
rows.name: Yes! I'll do my best!
